<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἄμμων Διονυσίῳ τῷ ἀδελφῷ 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐγὼ ἑκάστοτε ἡμέρας τὰ περὶ σοῦ 

    <lb n="4"/>ἐξετάζων οὐ διαλείπω τῆς σω-

    <lb n="5"/>τηρίας σου <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἕ</unclear>νεκεν, σὺ δὲ γράφων τῇ 

    <lb n="6"/>ἀδελφῇ μου περὶ ἐμοῦ <choice><corr>κ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">αὶ ἐ</supplied>ὰν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> ἅπαξ 

    <lb n="7"/>οὐκ ἐμνήσθης. ἕτοιμος οὖν ἤμην 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐλθεῖν πρὸς σὲ ἡνίκα ἤμην ἐν 

    <lb n="9"/>Βουβάστῳ, ἀλλ᾽ ἐπεί, ὡς πρόειπον, 

    <lb n="10"/>περὶ ἐμοῦ οὐδὲν ἐπέστειλας, διὰ 

    <lb n="11"/>τοῦτο ἐπέσχον. εἰ οὖν οἶδας ὅτι ἐπιθή-

    <lb n="12"/>κην εὑρίσκομεν παρὰ σοὶ ὥστε με-

    <lb n="13"/>ταβληθῆναι τὸ κερμάτιον ἐνθάδε, 

    <lb n="14"/>ἔρχομαι πρὸς σὲ εἰς συνωνὴν 

    <lb n="15"/>ἐρίων. νομίζω <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δὲ</unclear> ὅτι κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ</supplied> οἱ ἄλλοι 

    <lb n="16"/>βαφεῖς ἐκεῖ ἔρχονται τούτου ἕνε-

    <lb n="17"/>κα. αὐτῶν οὖν ἐλθόντων κοινώνη-

    <lb n="18"/>σον αὐτοῖς εἰς μέρος ἐμοὶ καὶ γράψον 

    <lb n="19"/>τινὶ θέλεις τὸ κερμάτιον μεταβαλῶ-

    <lb n="20"/>μαι. ἀσπάζεταί σε ἡ μήτηρ σου Πλου-

    <lb n="21"/>σίας καὶ ἡ ἀδελφή σου Ἑρμιόνη καὶ Ἀμοι-

    <lb n="22"/>τᾶς ὁ πατήρ σου καὶ Πατερμοῦθις ὁ ἀδελφός 

    <lb n="23"/>σου καὶ Παλλάς. ἀσπάσαι σὺ τὸν πατέ-

    <lb n="24"/>ρα ἀπό τε ἐμοῦ καὶ τῶν αὐτῶν. 

    <lb n="25"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὐχόμεθα παν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οι</unclear>-

    <lb n="26"/>κησίᾳ διὰ βίου πολλὰ πράσ-

    <lb n="27"/>σοντα. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><expan>ἀπό<ex cert="high">δος</ex></expan> Διονυσίῳ υἱῷ Παρμέν     οντος 

    <lb n="2"/><expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Ἄμμ</unclear>ωνος     πατρός. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.26658" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.26658" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="300" notBefore="101" type="textDate">II - III</date></p></div><div n="meta.26658" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Vgl. BASP 18, 1981, S. 80 - 81.</p></div><div n="meta.26658" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy. Hels.</title><biblScope type="numbers">48</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">26658</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0180</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">48</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0180;;48" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.26658" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">175</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.26658" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Plate 35</bibl><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Zilliacus, Papyrustutkimus, nach S. 112</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.26658" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="it"><head lang="de">Italienisch:</head><bibl default="NO" type="translations">